# 🤖 AI Impact on Jobs & Future Workforce Analytics (2020–2026)

## 📌 Project Overview

Artificial Intelligence is rapidly transforming industries by automating routine tasks, reshaping workforce requirements, and creating demand for new digital skills. This Power BI dashboard analyzes the impact of AI on jobs across multiple industries from **2020 to 2026**, providing business insights into automation risk, salary trends, AI adoption, workforce skill gaps, reskilling urgency, and future workforce demand.

The dashboard is designed to help business leaders, HR professionals, and decision-makers understand workforce transformation and develop proactive talent strategies for the future.

---

## 🎯 Business Objectives

- Assess automation exposure across different industries.
- Evaluate the impact of AI on employee salary growth.
- Analyze AI adoption across industries.
- Identify workforce skill gaps and future skill requirements.
- Evaluate reskilling urgency and AI disruption intensity.
- Support workforce planning through data-driven insights and recommendations.

